## Our Discovery Engine Integrates Simulation, AI, and Robotics
Our platform integrates four key assets to provide an end-to-end solution, from fundamental prediction to real-world production.

<div class="card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>The AI Engine</h3>
    <p>Our revolutionary deep-learning model delivers unprecedented predictive accuracy to rapidly explore complex chemical systems and de-risk industrial R&D.</p>
    <a href="/platform/ai-breakthrough/">Learn More &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>The Discovery Engine</h3>
    <p>A <strong>$2.7M national robotics network</strong> that automates experimentation, guided by our unique expertise in quantum simulation at the UNE node.</p>
    <a href="/platform/discovery-engine/">Learn More &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Proven Impact</h3>
    <p>Our capabilities are demonstrated in high-impact projects, including a global water solution developed with <a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.2508208122" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nobel Laureate Sir Kostya Novoselov</a>
    <a href="/platform/solutions/">Learn More &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>





## What We Solve
<div class="card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>E-Waste & Critical Materials Recovery</h3>
    <p>Unlock value from complex waste streams. We design processes to efficiently recover precious metals and recycle components from solar panels and batteries.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Biofuel & Biowaste Valorization</h3>
    <p>Transform agricultural and industrial waste into high-value fuels and chemicals. Our platform rapidly optimizes conversion pathways for maximum yield and efficiency.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Custom Sustainable Chemistry</h3>
    <p>Have a different challenge? Our engine is adaptable. Let's design a custom solution for your unique materials or process development needs.</p>
  </div>
</div>



